Sinnertwin bounds out of the line of fire, further away from all the
explosions. One of his head keeps an eye on his direction, while the
other turns, and opens it's maw. A stream of fire bursts out, sending a
ball of searing flame towards the passing jets.

(This is it guys, just like the Terrorcons against the Technobots :)
